                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Brussels</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-04-08"><hi rend="italic">April 8,
                                1908</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Memorandum in the sense of department’s telegram of April 1 with minister
